:

*Zabavi* se na plaži. (Have fun at the beach.)
Ona je *zabavila* svoje prijatelje. (She entertained her friends.)
Ona se *zabavlja* svaki dan. (She is having fun every day.)
Svi su se *zabavili* na proslavi. (Everyone had fun at the celebration.)
Oni su se *zabavili* do kasno u noć. (They had fun until late at night.)